metadata.name: Artist Anonymous #1
metadata.description: In shadows' veil, the artist's heart beats still, Their secrets shared in verses of goodwill. To find their handle, start with double I, Then four l's, their tweet identity to spy.  Now join three I's, and let the pattern swell, Five l's in line, their hidden truth to tell. Combine the parts, a sequence to unfurl, Their Twitter handle, gateway to their world.  Seek the art, let whispered words set sail, Unlock the door, embrace the cryptic tale. For in their work, the deepest magic thrives, Discover now, the artist's secret lives.
